sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend as Frontend UI
    participant ApiEndpoints as Frontend API Endpoints
    participant Backend as Backend API
    participant Auth as Auth Service

    User->>Frontend: Open feature requiring data
    activate Frontend
    Frontend->>ApiEndpoints: requestResource(params)
    activate ApiEndpoints
    ApiEndpoints->>Auth: validateSession(token)
    activate Auth
    Auth-->>ApiEndpoints: sessionValid
    deactivate Auth
    ApiEndpoints->>Backend: GET /resource?params
    activate Backend
    Backend-->>ApiEndpoints: 200 OK (data)
    deactivate Backend
    ApiEndpoints-->>Frontend: return data
    deactivate ApiEndpoints
    Frontend-->>User: Render data
    deactivate Frontend